335
0:15:48,000 --> 0:15:5,000
we could probably attract

336
0:15:5,000 --> 0:15:52,000
four to six billion dollars

337
0:15:52,000 --> 0:15:54,000
quite easily in the textile sector,

338
0:15:54,000 --> 0:15:56,000
if there was zero tariffs --

339
0:15:56,000 --> 0:15:59,000
would create the type of job.

340
0:15:59,000 --> 0:16:02,000
